        <dl>
          <dt class="title is-5">Operator</dt>
          <dd class="content">A team member</dd>

          <dt class="title is-5">Lead Operator</dt>
          <dd class="content">An operator who has full strategy management.</dd>

          <dt class="title is-5">Commander</dt>
          <dd class="content">An operator with full strategy & team
          management.</dd>
          
          <dt class="title is-5">Freelancer</dt>
          <dd class="content">An operator that has either not been assigned an
          objective or has already completed all of its assigned objectives. </dd>
        </dl>
